titles.title: A bill to modify the provisions relating to formulations of Ethanediamide, N-(2-ethoxyphenyl)-N'-(2-ethylphenyl)-).

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/19/2006--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to modify the provisions relating to formulations of Ethanediamide, N-(2-ethoxyphenyl)-N'-(2-ethylphenyl)-), and to suspend, through December 31, 2009, the duty on them.
